        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Q: Does SaneBox work with my email provider?",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "A:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Yes. It works with any IMAP email service, including Gmail, Outlook, Yahoo, AOL, iCloud, and company servers. It’s client-agnostic, meaning it works seamlessly whether you use an app on your phone, a desktop client, or webmail.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Q: Is my email data secure with SaneBox?",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "A:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " SaneBox takes security seriously. It only processes email headers and metadata (like sender, subject, and date) to make its decisions. It does not read the body of your private emails. Your email credentials are never stored, and all communication is encrypted.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Q: What if I don’t like what it filters?",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "A:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " SaneBox learns from you. If an important email ends up in @SaneLater, simply drag it back to your Inbox. SaneBox will instantly remember that preference for the future. You are always in control, and the system improves with every interaction.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
